data.description: Step into the world of real estate ownership with this four-bedroom, three-bathroom home that offers not only a comfortable living space but also the promise of future equity growth. Imagine watching your investment and the value of your home increase over time. By applying sweat equity and undertaking home improvement projects, this home could become the cornerstone of your financial future.Gary, Indiana offers a variety of attractions to enjoy. Here are some notable attractions in the area:Indiana Dunes Beach & National Park,Michael Jackson Family Home,Majestic Star Casino,The Steel Yard,Marquette Park and Pavilion,Gary SouthShore RailCats,andLake Street Beach.This property offers a prime location that brings you closer to everything you need, from shopping atSouthLake Mall, Costco, WalMart, to dining atrestaurants such asCooper's Hawk, Chili's, Chipotle,Chick-fil-A.Additionally, you'll enjoy effortless travel via major highways I-65 and HWY 80/94.
